  m_Name: Tut_ClueNote2_Page2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  type: 0
  text: "Whatever you do, do not let yourself fall into the dark. Not even for a
    moment. It is not just absence, it's hunger. And it remembers you.\n\nI thought
    I could outrun it.\nI thought I could outthink it.\n\nNow I understand\u2026
    it doesn\u2019t chase you.\nIt replaces you.\n\nIf you feel yourself growing
    tired, if your thoughts start to echo back wrong, turn back while you still can.
    The maze does not forgive hesitation.\n\nI can hear it now. Inside the walls.
    Inside me.\n\nIt\u2019s too late for me."
  texture: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fe28bf42f38b7c44d8174dffa2650480, type: 3}
